    <p> In another area of &#8203;&#8203;the museum, we found out about unwanted immigrants such as rats and other animals. How these have come in and what a threat they represent for local flora and fauna. In the end it went through an art gallery and a peculiar private collection of various jugs, vases and porcelain. </p>
    <p> After we were through the exhibition in the late afternoon, we decided to visit the city. </p>
